          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Determination of neutron-induced alpha-particle cross",
                " sections on carbon using the response of a liquid",
                " scintillation detector"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "2GERPTB"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The PTB energy-variable",
                "                compact cyclotron."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-D"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "   A nanosecond pulsed deuteron beam was incident",
                " on a deuterium gas target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Main peak plus a breakup continuum. The latter was",
                " separated by TOF techniques."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".The NE-213 scintillators were simultaneously used as",
                " carbon samples and hydrogen monitor samples."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PSD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "   N-gamma discrimination was applied."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  Two different NE-213 scintillation detectors",
                " were used, one being 2 inch diameter by 2 inch thick",
                " and the other 4 inch diameter by 4 inch thick. They",
                " were encapsulated in aluminum housings and coupled via",
                " specially designed light pipes to fast multipliers.",
                " The detectors were positioned 12 m downstream from the",
                " neutron target behind a collimator system at an angle",
                " of 0 degrees to the direction of the deuteron beam.",
                " To obtain a large dynamic range, two gain factors",
                " were used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".The detector response functions were calculated with",
                " the MONTE CARLO code NRESP, version 5. Cross sections",
                " for these calculations were taken from ENDF/B-V."
              ]
            }
          ],
